  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Soaking meshes in a vancomycin solution just prior to their use in open hernia repairs will
      decrease rates of mesh infection
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
  <start_date>June 2013</start_date>
